他們規規矩矩，不許他們亂說亂動。如要亂說亂動，立即取締，予以制裁。」[2]"},{"pid":"e3612f937bd6ee80a415974dda18a5e4f66f0418","tid":1614241,"uid":103598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b10a63aef8cceea7d0a4fefefc0b77270f840fba","tid":1614241,"uid":137912,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:28:44.000Z","msg":"食住關班狗咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T17:56:42.000Z","msg":"佢地份糧我地有份出嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}